temp.fibHeap.stixar.graph.paths
Class PathFinder

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Filtering
public class PathFinder
extends DFS.Visitor
implements Filtering

A simple reachability class for computing a small number of reachability queries.

If many reachability computations are required, and the Path of reachability is not needed for the queries, one should consider using stixar.graph.conn.Transitivity as it will be more efficient.
